OL,3,CZack Polanski apologises after failing
OL,4,Cto pay correct houseboat council tax
OL,6,FLeader of the Green Party, Zack
OL,7,FPolanski, has admitted he may have
OL,8,Ffailed to pay the correct council tax
OL,9,Fwhile living on a houseboat in London.
OL,11,FPolanski had faced mounting questions
OL,12,Fover whether the houseboat, moored in
OL,13,Feast London, was his primary residence.
OL,15,FA Green Party spokesperson described
OL,16,Fthe situation as an "unintentional
OL,17,Fmistake" and said he had "immediately
OL,18,Ftaken steps" to pay any tax owed.
OL,26,@xD@UOUyD@HO]yD@ZOUzD@LO]
