OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778637819
OL,3,CZack Polanski apologises after failing
OL,4,Cto pay correct houseboat council tax
OL,6,F"Until relatively recently, Zack was
OL,7,Fliving on a houseboat, which came with
OL,8,Fits own unique practical circumstances
OL,9,Fand considerations.
OL,11,F"He has immediately taken steps to pay
OL,12,Fany council tax he may be found to
OL,13,Fowe. Zack apologises sincerely for the
OL,14,Funintentional mistake."
OL,16,FThe Green Party previously told The
OL,17,FTimes newspaper that Polanski rented a
OL,18,Froom at another address where council
OL,19,Ftax was included in the rent and only
OL,20,Fstayed on the boat "occasionally".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@WO]|D@TOU|D@aO]
