OL,3,CZack Polanski apologises after failing
OL,4,Cto pay correct houseboat council tax
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FGovernment guidance states that a
OL,12,Fperson may be liable for council tax
OL,13,Fon a boat if it is their "sole or
OL,14,Fmain" residence.
OL,16,FA Green Party spokesperson added: "For
OL,17,Fsecurity reasons, we do not comment
OL,18,Fpublicly on Zack's address.
OL,26,@uD@ZOUvD@EO]xD@cOU
