OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778637819
OL,3,CZack Polanski apologises after failing
OL,4,Cto pay correct houseboat council tax
OL,6,FThe Daily Mail separately reported
OL,7,Fthat Polanski was registered to vote
OL,8,Fat a building near the marina, which
OL,9,Fhe is also said to have used as a
OL,10,Fmailing address.
OL,12,FTax lawyer Dan Neidle, founder of Tax
OL,13,FPolicy Associates, analysed Polanski's
OL,14,Fsituation this week and wrote: "If the
OL,15,Fboat was in fact Mr Polanski's 'sole
OL,16,For main residence' then he and/or his
OL,17,Fpartner should have registered for,
OL,18,Fand paid, council tax for those three
OL,19,Fyears."
OL,26,@vD@`OU{D@GO]
